-Install playonlinux
	pac playonlinux

-Ater install go to playonlinux>configure, select office 2010 drive, click on>wine version and > change to 1.7.52

-Clicke configure> select 2010 office drive > Miscellaneous > run an .exe on this drive > select the Activator

-In activator app click tab > Addition > type 127.0.0.2 > connect to server > keep this app opened

-Back to playonlinux > install > office > Office 2010 activation > install > next > volume activation kms > type 127.0.0.2 > next > type 1688 > next > yes

-Playonlinux > open and close word 2 times, second time should activate it

-Close all
